Storage Structure:

keyspace column-family['row-key']['super-column']['column'] = 'value';

Facebook: Comments more likes (like count):
facebook_comment_like_count[comment-id][post-id][user-id] = 'like-count';

Facebook: Most popular users post (like count / comment count):
facebook_post_user_popular[post-id][user-id][comments-count] = 'like-count';

Facebook: Most popular page post (like count / comment count):
facebook_post_page_popular[post-id][page-id][comments-count] = 'like-count';